# {{name}}

{{#if scope}}> {{scope}}{{/if}}

Monorepo managed with [Moon](https://moonrepo.dev) and [Proto](https://moonrepo.dev/proto).

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install runtimes (if using Node/pnpm)
proto install

# Install dependencies (if using pnpm)
pnpm install
```

## Structure

- `apps/` - Applications
- `packages/` - Shared packages
- `modules/` - Modules
- `scripts/` - Scripts
- `tools/` - Tool configurations

## Commands

```bash
# Scaffold new app
aikuora scaffold &lt;tool&gt; --name &lt;name&gt;

# Link tool to target
aikuora link &lt;tool&gt; &lt;target&gt;

# Show monorepo info
aikuora info
```
